snippet.title: Will the New Johnny Depp Amber Heard Court Case Delay Aquaman 2?
snippet.description:
Will the New Johnny Depp Amber Heard Court Case Delay Aquaman 2?

The judge granted Johnny Depp's trial delay request in his upcoming case against Amber Heard, which means it won't conflict with his Fantastic Beasts 3 filming.

But pushing up the trail date COULD cause a scheduling conflict with Amber Heard's Aquaman 2 filming if the case runs long in May 2021.
